<lb n="0408b13" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">二合</note>　哥<note place="inline">引</note>　尾舍<note n="0408006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＋（合二）細註【明】</note><note n="0408006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，二<note place="inline">合二</note>【明】</note><app n="0408006"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">二合二</note></rdg></app></p>
