<lb n="0408b17" ed="T"/>哥<note place="inline">引</note>　商尾說嚕<note place="inline">引</note>　波<note place="inline">引</note>　提底瑟姹<note place="inline">二合</note>　<g ref="#CB00805"/><note n="0408007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【三】</note><note n="0408007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0408007"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0408b18" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0408b1801" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「所有三摩地大印，<caesura/>依法若能正一結，</l>
<lb n="0408b19" ed="T"/><l>隨執蓮華授與時，<caesura/>彼即常施敬愛法，</l>
<lb n="0408b20" ed="T"/><l>所有大智三昧印，<caesura/>依法若能正一結。</l></lg>
<lb n="0408b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0408b2101">「<note n="0408008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（此等…結）三百三十四字∞（次當…身法）三百三十五字【三】【宮】</note><note n="0408008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（次當…身法）三百三十五字【大】∞（此等…結）三百三十四字【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>次當教授智出生法：</p>
<lb n="0408b22" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0408b2201" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「觀自在尊相合故，<caesura/>觀想蓮華現於心，</l>
<lb n="0408b23" ed="T"/><l>得彼蓮華三摩地，<caesura/>剎那速疾能發起。</l>
<lb n="0408b24" ed="T"/><l>觀自在尊相合故，<caesura/>觀想蓮華現於額，</l>
<lb n="0408b25" ed="T"/><l>彼慣習法堅固成，<caesura/>剎那即能空中行。</l>
<lb n="0408b26" ed="T"/><l>觀自在尊三摩地，<caesura/>觀想蓮華現於舌，</l>
<lb n="0408b27" ed="T"/><l>由彼速疾成就因，<caesura/>剎那即能騰空去。</l>
<lb n="0408b28" ed="T"/><l>觀自在尊三摩地，<caesura/>觀想蓮華現於頂，</l>
<pb n="0408c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0408c"/>
<lb n="0408c01" ed="T"/><l>由彼速疾成就因，<caesura/>剎那上踴而自在。</l></lg>
<lb n="0408c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0408c0201">「此等大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0408c03" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c0301">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>　那紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>　捺野<note place="inline">引</note>　尾舍
<lb n="0408c04" ed="T"/><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c05" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c0501">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>　那<note place="inline">引</note>　毘始<note place="inline">引</note>　酤<note place="inline">引</note>　尾舍
<lb n="0408c06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c07" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c0701">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>　那尾捺踰<note place="inline">二合引</note>　怛摩<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0408c08" ed="T"/>尾舍<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c09" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c0901">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>　那烏瑟膩<note place="inline">二合引</note>　沙<note place="inline">引</note>　尾
<lb n="0408c10" ed="T"/>舍<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c11" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0408c1101" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「若在虛空若餘方，<caesura/>蓮華影像當觀想，</l>
<lb n="0408c12" ed="T"/><l>由此法儀成就因，<caesura/>剎那即得隱身法。</l>
<lb n="0408c13" ed="T"/><l>若在虛空若餘方，<caesura/>蓮華影像當觀想，</l>
<lb n="0408c14" ed="T"/><l>自身想成彼蓮華，<caesura/>剎那即得隱身法。</l>
<lb n="0408c15" ed="T"/><l>若在虛空若餘方，<caesura/>蓮華影像當觀想，</l>
<lb n="0408c16" ed="T"/><l>隨見隨取彼蓮華，<caesura/>速疾成就隱身法。</l>
<lb n="0408c17" ed="T"/><l>若在虛空若餘方，<caesura/>蓮華影像當觀想，</l>
<lb n="0408c18" ed="T"/><l>見已想取蓮華食，<caesura/>剎那即得隱身法。</l>
<lb n="0408c19" ed="T"/><l>隨應當執於蓮華，<caesura/>即得施諸敬愛法，</l>
<lb n="0408c20" ed="T"/><l>三摩地印善如儀，<caesura/>依法若能正一結，</l>
<lb n="0408c21" ed="T"/><l>隨應授彼智蓮華，<caesura/>而彼速施敬愛法，</l>
<lb n="0408c22" ed="T"/><l>所有羯磨三昧印，<caesura/>依法若能正一結，</l>
<lb n="0408c23" ed="T"/><l>隨欲授於敬愛時，<caesura/>剎那速得<note n="0408009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＝於【宋】</note><note n="0408009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施【大】，於【宋】</note><app n="0408009"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">於</rdg></app>蓮華。</l></lg>
<lb n="0408c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0408c2401">「此等大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0408c25" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c2501">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　呼<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c26" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c2601">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　三摩野鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　呼<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c27" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c2701">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　倪也<note place="inline">二合<note n="0408010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0408010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0408010"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>　那鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　呼<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0408c28" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0408c2801">「唵<note place="inline">引</note>　葛哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　鉢訥摩<note place="inline">二合</note>　呼<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline"><note n="0408011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝二【宮】</note><note n="0408011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，二【宮】</note><app n="0408011"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">二</rdg></app>句</note></p>
<pb n="0409a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0409a"/>
<lb n="0409a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0409a0101">「復次，教授智曼拏羅大印智法：</p>
<lb n="0409a02" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0409a0201" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「依法曼拏羅法用，<caesura/>大印如儀作成就，</l>
<lb n="0409a03" ed="T"/><l>我今總略而敷宣，<caesura/>最勝三昧印相合，</l>
<lb n="0409a04" ed="T"/><l>依法曼拏羅法用，<caesura/>蓮華位中安蓮華，</l>
<lb n="0409a05" ed="T"/><l>法三昧拳二羽成，<caesura/>所作羯磨如儀軌。」</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0409a06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="020" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說一切如來真實攝大乘現證三昧大教王
<lb n="0409a07" ed="T"/>經卷第二十</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>